highlights.text: “你，好不好？ - TVBS連續劇【遺憾拼圖】片尾曲” by Eric Chou has been on Top Songs Singapore the longest, at 3161 days straight.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Singapore. “Cruel Summer” is the highest at #45.
“Fortnight (feat. Post Malone)” by Taylor Swift and Post Malone is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Singapore, up 84 spots at #94.
“善后” by 马师傅 is the highest new entry on Top Songs Singapore at #157.
